<dl><dt> <span class="script">template.XULAttr("hidecolumnpicker")</span> </dt><dd> Type: <em>boolean</em> </dd><dd> When set to <code>false</code>, a drop-down will appear in the upper right corner of the <span class="script">template.XULElem("tree")</span>, which the user may use to show and hide columns. When set to <code>true</code>, the column picker will be hidden. The default value is <code>false</code>. </dd></dl>
